synopsis: Live Video of a performance by Sara Hook of her piece Caucasian Spirituals, the piece showcases the conflicts of being a young southern woman while wanting to free herself to the current cultural norms of the northern cities.

casting: ['Inácio Netto', 'Vitória Bacelar', 'Kaio Kylua', 'Marília dos Santos', 'Renan Junio', 'Sophia Magalhães', 'Silvia Campos']
